        <abstract> 
<p>Has learned that German edition [of <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>] will be on larger pages than English one. No copies of heliotype plates [for <hi rend="italic">Expression</hi>] have been delivered. Hopes Heliotype Company is not going to throw them over. Suggests CD write a strong letter.</p> 
        </abstract>
